Choose the path of the "Before Image" Directory. 
In this directory all before image files are stored. They enable 
application-initiated transaction abort and database recovery 
after machine crash.
The total size of before image files is the sum of all pages 
changed by the current transactions.  

NOTE: If this directory is placed on a NFS mounted file system, 
	crash recovery is not reliable!


   -	Command Line Syntax :  bf=<path>
